in FHIR R4.

The source element is defined as:
`ConceptMap.group` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Across FHIR versions, the element set has been mapped as:
*  R5: `ConceptMap.group` 0..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4B: `ConceptMap.group` 0..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4: `ConceptMap.group` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Following are the generation technical comments:
Element `ConceptMap.group` has is mapped to FHIR R4 element `ConceptMap.group`, but has no comparisons."/>
